  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Spiagge San Pietro holiday village is a great holiday choice for those in search of the perfect beach and plenty of relaxation. Situated just 45 minutes’ drive from Cagliari airport in a peaceful location, it provides comfortable accommodation on an All-Inclusive basis which represents great value for money.</p>
<p>The beach of fine white sand, equipped with sunbeds and umbrellas, is 300m away down a path and the turquoise sea is gently shelving and perfect for swimming and snorkeling. There is a water sports centre 3kms away where you can hire pedaloes, windsurfs and kayaks. Sail boat excursions along the coast can also be booked at a local charge.</p>
<p>The central resort area houses the reception, restaurant and bar whereas rooms are spread out around the pleasant grounds. Guest bedrooms are decorated in cool Mediterranean style and have air conditioning and a terrace if on the ground floor or a balcony if on the first floor. Family rooms have a double room and interconnecting twin bedroom and one bathroom. Junior Suites are located above the bar.</p>]]></description>
