  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<p>The children’s club is for 3-11 year olds and provides a programme of activities and entertainment and there’s also a ‘Jek Club’ for 12-17 year olds that organises sports competitions such as archery and beach volley. The clubs are predominantly Italian speaking but some English is spoken.</p>]]></familyDescription>
